N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 530.9 - Order of the court

State Regulations

The order of the court, together with the
record filed with the court, shall be entered and filed in the clerk's office
at Court of Appeals Hall in Albany. Notes
